'''ChaPanda × Zenless Zone Zero''' is a collaborative effort between ''[[Zenless Zone Zero]]'' creators [[miHoYo]] and {{w|ChaPanda}}.

==Collaborations==
To date, there has been '''1''' collaborations between ''Zenless Zone Zero'' and ChaPanda.

===2025===
This collaboration features ChaPanda drinks with a [[Orphie Magnusson & Magus]] and [[Seed]] themed menu. 
* When purchased the special menu set, physical collectibles can be obtained, such as:
** Acrylic key chain Accessories
** Badges
** Acrylic figure stands
** Laser tickets

